    "Bottle of Water helps you drink regularly: quick logging, live progress, widgets and Apple Health sync. Nothing extra." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bottle of Water hilft dir, regelmäßig zu trinken: schnelles Protokollieren, Live-Fortschritt, Widgets und Apple-Health-Sync. Nichts Überflüssiges."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bottle of Water te ayuda a beber con regularidad: registro rápido, progreso en vivo, widgets y sincronización con Apple Health. Nada más."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bottle of Water vous aide à boire régulièrement : enregistrement rapide, progression en direct, widgets et synchro Apple Health. Rien de superflu."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bottle of Water ti aiuta a bere con regolarità: registro rapido, progressi in tempo reale, widget e sincronizzazione con Apple Health. Nient'altro."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bottle of Waterは規則的な水分補給をサポート：素早い記録、リアルタイムの進捗、ウィジェット、Apple Health同期。余計なものはなし。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bottle of Water는 규칙적인 수분 섭취를 도와요: 빠른 기록, 실시간 진행률, 위젯, Apple 건강 동기화. 군더더기 없이."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "O Bottle of Water ajuda você a beber com regularidade: registro rápido, progresso ao vivo, widgets e sincronização com o Apple Health. Nada a mais."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bottle of Water помогает пить воду регулярно: быстрое логирование, живой прогресс, виджеты и синхронизация с Apple Health. Ничего лишнего."
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bottle of Water düzenli su içmene yardım eder: hızlı kayıt, canlı ilerleme, widget'lar ve Apple Health eşitlemesi. Fazlası yok."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bottle of Water 帮你规律饮水：快速记录、实时进度、小组件和 Apple 健康同步。别无冗余。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
